data.description: Presenting this 2019-built home, featuring a roof, HVAC system, water heater, and major appliances all under 5 years old! The interior finishes are simply captivating, with an open floor plan seamlessly connecting the livingroom, den, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a wonderful flow. The gourmet kitchen boasts marble counters, counter-height seating, stainless steel appliances, and custom cabinetry. Enjoy privacy in the primary suite, complete with an oversized custom-tiled walk-in shower and spacious walk-in closet. Two additional guest rooms and a guest bathroom offer ample space. A fenced backyard, covered patio, and off-street parking complete the package. It's a must-see!
